her than localized moments. These 4$d$ conduction bands are polarized\nin the region of the Fermi energy and mediate the interaction between the\nlocalized rare earth moments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Oct 2009 17:50:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 14 Oct 2009 20:56:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-14"}
