 unfolded proteins.\nThese proteins reasonably have physical properties intermediate between those\nof folded and those of natively unfolded proteins and their structural\nproperties and evolutionary history are worth to be investigated.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Oct 2009 15:18:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 19 Oct 2009 10:17:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-08"}
